{"about_the_game":"<strong>CarLife Simulator</strong> is a realistic car driving simulator with fun and challenges for the driver. Ideal for learning how to drive a car in different conditions, off-road, cities, racing tracks for every taste, all this is available in <strong>CarLife Simulator</strong>.<br><br><strong>Cars</strong>. Over 40 vehicles, each unique, from family sedans to rare hypercars. <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342610/extras/4FOTCA.png?t=1722008962\" /><br><br><strong>Game world</strong>. An open world with a big city, interesting places full of secrets, beautiful views from the top of a mountain, or a crystal clear lake far from civilization. Racing tracks that challenge you to complete the lap as quickly as possible. <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342610/extras/3FOTCA.png?t=1722008962\" /><br><br><strong>Realistic and smart AI</strong>. It is present in the game world in the form of traffic, but also in the form of rivals on the track.  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342610/extras/1FOTCA.png?t=1722008962\" /><br><br><strong>Quests</strong>. From racing with merciless rivals who strive to cut and leave you behind, to passing the track for a certain time on a wet track where you have to prove your skills in combat with your car.  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342610/extras/7FOTCA.png?t=1722008962\" /><br><br><strong>Photorealistic graphics</strong>. Draws you into the game more, which makes the atmosphere even more interesting and immerses you in dozens of hours of exploring the game world.  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342610/extras/2FOTCA.png?t=1722008962\" /><br><br><strong>Gamepad and steering wheel support</strong>. By connecting your device, you can feel like a real driver. You can drive both automatic transmission and manual. <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342610/extras/5FOTCA.png?t=1722008962\" /><br><br><strong>Attention to detail</strong>. All maps are made in detail, as well as cars. Each model is unique, each map has different interesting places and easter eggs. Cars are as close to reality as possible.  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342610/extras/8FOTCA.png?t=1722008962\" /><br><br><strong>Photo mode</strong>. Realistic photo mode that allows you to take beautiful photos inside the game.  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342610/extras/6FOTCA.png?t=1722008962\" /><br><br><strong>Regular updates</strong>. Every month updates are released where new cars, maps, quests, and many different goodies are added.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342610/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1722008962","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342610/page.bg.jpg?t=1722008962","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342610/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1722008962","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342610/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1722008962","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<strong>CarLife Simulator</strong> is a realistic car driving simulator with fun and challenges for the driver. Ideal for learning how to drive a car in different conditions, off-road, cities, racing tracks for every taste, all this is available in <strong>CarLife Simulator</strong>.<br><br><stro